%section#features
  .container-fluid
    %h2.sr-only Features and Testimonials

    %figure.testimonial
      %blockquote
        :kramdown
          We used Statto to help select the Dutch national mixed team for WCBU and sent trialees screenshots of their individual stats afterwards. The feedback was overwhelmingly positive. I'm very impressed with the app.
      %figcaption
        .testimonial-name David Sparks, WUGC ‘16 Netherlands Open, WCBU ‘17 Netherlands Mixed
        = retina_image_tag "david-sparks.jpg", class: 'testimonial-avatar rounded-circle', alt: 'David Sparks', width: 80, height: 80

    .feature.row
      .col-md-4.push-md-8
        :kramdown
          ###Real-time Insights

          Quickly switch views during a time-out to see live stats for the game you are tracking. Pitch heatmaps, pass completion rate, scoring efficiency percentages and more can help you make informed tactical decisions on the sideline.
      .col-md-8.pull-md-4
        = retina_image_tag 'heatmap.png', class: 'img-fluid'

    .feature.row
      .col-md-4
        :kramdown
          ###Simple Player Selection

          During half-time, check how players are performing to gauge their pitch-time. Filter players by how many points they've played to see who needs to get on and who's being overworked.

          Sort players into groups like 'D Line' or 'Handlers' to make selecting who is on the line a breeze.

      .col-md-8
        = retina_image_tag 'player-profile.png', class: 'img-fluid'

    .feature.row
      .col-md-4.push-md-8
        :kramdown
          ###Pitch-level Detail

          Simply tap on the pitch to record the locations of passes, blocks, stall outs and more with less effort than tallying on paper.

          No video footage from a muddy battle on Pitch 14? No problem. Review games back at home by scrolling through the Play By Play and see everything drawn on the pitch.

      .col-md-8.pull-md-4
        = retina_image_tag 'tracker.png', class: 'img-fluid img-bordered', width: 700, height: 396

    %figure.testimonial
      %blockquote
        :kramdown
          The UAE national team was heading to Amman to play in the MENA 2016 championships so I thought I would give Statto a try. It's super slick. Seriously great. Quick and easy to use which is key to following a game and recording stats.
      %figcaption
        .testimonial-name Patrick Fourcampre-Maye, WCBU ‘17 UAE Mixed
        = retina_image_tag "patrick-fourcampre-maye.jpg", class: 'testimonial-avatar rounded-circle', alt: 'Patrick Fourcampre-Maye', width: 80, height: 80


