%section#stats
  .container-fluid
    %h2.text-center Insights Provided by Statto

    .row.stat-lists
      .col-md-4
        %h3.text-md-center Game
        :kramdown
          - Full play-by-play for review, with each possession drawn out on a pitch map
          - Point difference over the course of the game
          - Scoring efficiency for O and D per point or possession
          - Defensive turnover efficiency
          - Pass completion
          - Point recovery rate (likelihood of scoring having turned over)
          - Heatmaps of assist attempts, defensive blocks and incomplete throws

      .col-md-4
        %h3.text-md-center Player
        :kramdown
          - Box score of basic stats like points played, touches, goals, assists, blocks and turnovers
          - Plus/minus score
          - Radar chart of role and impact relative to teammates
          - Scoring efficiency on O and D
          - Defensive turnover efficiency
          - Throw completion
          - Offensive ultization (percentage of points played with touches)
          - Heatmaps of assists, defensive blocks and turnovers

      .col-md-4
        %h3.text-md-center Team
        :kramdown
          - Win/loss ratio
          - Scored/conceded ratio
          - Turnover rate per point
          - Top players by assists, goals, blocks and pitch time
          - Scoring efficiency for O and D per point or possession
          - Defensive turnover efficiency
          - Pass completion
          - Point recovery rate (likelihood of scoring having turned over)

    %h3.text-center Plus fine-grained detail in CSV exports and more charts in the works!

